raction has been proven to perform better in case of\ndynamic viewpoint videos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2019 18:14:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 18:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
