, and\nthen applying Barbour's generator approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Oct 2019 05:23:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Jul 2020 05:38:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-07"}
