 that L-Platooning\nhandles seamlessly the vehicle join and leave maneuvers for a long platoon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Oct 2019 13:57:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 May 2020 22:46:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 21:19:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-25"}
